title: Lupin the 3rd: World's Most Wanted (Volume 1)
description: Lupin, the suave thief who makes a habit of stealing from the rich and keeping the spoils for himself, embarks on a new sequence of heists in this anime TV series. Joined by Jigen, a master marksman, and Goemon, a fierce samurai, Lupin jaunts around the world, lining his pockets and eluding Interpol Inspector Zenigata. But when Lupin&#039;s sometime rival Fujiko appears, he must be extra wary of her mischievous traps.
